Dick Martin (comedian) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dick_Martin_(comedian) 0 Thomas Richard Martin (January 30, 1922 – May 24, 2008), known professionally as Dick Martin, was an American comedian and director. He was known for his role as the co-host of the sketch comedy program Rowan Martin's Laugh-In from 1968-73.
